e=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">道路以外 仲有 鐵路 做後備</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"2e124b3de8e44069a8517a3641ef763534beebad","tid":1402834,"uid":267942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T17:12:28.000Z","msg":"沒有氣餒的本錢，必須加強文宣<br />\n<br />\n夢遊時要幫手提供安全撒離路線， 附近道路情況<br />\n<br />\n日落時間，尾班車時間， 尾班前60分鐘開始溫馨提示<br />\n<br />\n多人中離開，被人圍，起碼多街坊聲援。<br />\n<br />\n一定要至少留2條退走比自己走<br />\n<br />\n不受傷 不被補 不戀戰 不割蓆 各自爬山 一齊黎 一齊走"},{"pid":"e321497ca69b6d80c68cb0ba845ef53b2bb04355","tid":1402834,"uid":276273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T17:30:00.000Z","msg":"黑社會的日常，夜晚先活動"},{"pid":"7a5a1d0915e87fa5c415e91f9137a67ec61de059","tid":1402834,"uid":6435,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T17:32:01.000Z","msg":"本民前都講過呢樣野<br />\n一到夜晚佢地大量資源既優勢就會極度明顯"},{"pid":"0621443f740ac482ca49a578489ebb979df80c97","tid":1402834,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T16:37:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5139d341c2d09147c782aa06b9d38419831435ba","tid":1402834,"uid":78420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c034f86d38958fc59eba04d73ec83a0a8e094ca6","tid":1402834,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T17:04:32.000Z","msg":"如果一街都係車 警察調動會變得好慢<br />\n呢個都係其中一個夜晚出動警察既好處"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T16:51:33.000Z","msg":"還有義士溶入人群中易D。"}]}